behavior wash_shirt(shirt:item, sink:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inside(shirt, sink)
        # Ensure the shirt is placed in the sink

        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            # If the sink has a faucet, turn it on to wet the shirt

        wash(shirt) # Wash the shirt

        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)
            # If the sink has a faucet, turn it off after washing

behavior rinse_shirt(shirt:item, sink:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inside(shirt, sink)
        # Ensure the shirt is placed in the sink

        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            # If the sink has a faucet, turn it on to rinse the shirt

        rinse(shirt) # Rinse the shirt

        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)
            # If the sink has a faucet, turn it off after rinsing
